    <h2>The transcription workflow</h2>
    <p>Key: CC tasks, <span class="sc">SC tasks</span>, <span class="tr">Transcriber tasks</span>.</p> 
    <ol>
      <li>Identify source of needed Images.</li>
      <li>Inform the SWAT team&#160;</li>
      <li>Upload onto Image Server and label in standard format.</li>
      <li>View sample Images to check: language / image quality / readability.</li>
      <li>Record on Register Record.</li>
      <li>Assign to SC.</li>
      <li class="sc">Receive assignment of images.</li>
      <li class="tr">Register as a Transcriber if not already done. Note: only 1 UserID per person and 1 Syndicate Coordinator per person.</li>
      <li class="tr">Review Place Names [on RAP] and identify Availability of images. Request from SC.</li>
      <li class="sc">Receive request for a batch of images from Transcriber who has searched the RAP.</li>
      <li class="sc">Scan Image Server for chosen place name. Request allocation of new Images batch for particular Transcriber.</li>
      <li class="sc">Request allocation by CC of chosen Images for Transcriber.</li>
      <li class="sc">Allocate requested Images. Update Register records.</li>
      <li class="sc">Advise Transcriber. If new, monitor their progress / ability. Revise allocation if necessary or request checks as necessary.</li>
      <li class="tr">Transcribe allocated Images. Seek help from SC if necessary. Pass to SC for review if requested.</li>
      <li class="sc">Check Transcription when image batch (or designated portion if new transcriber) is complete.</li>
      <li class="sc">Agree whether Transcriber can upload themselves or upload on their behalf.</li>
      <li class="tr">Upload own Transcription. Tell SC if this is part or whole of the allocated set.</li>
      <li class="sc">Rectify errors or return to Transcriber.</li>
      <li class="tr">Rectify errors in conjunction with SC.</li>
      <li class="sc">When whole bundle of Images is transcribed and uploaded, advise CC to update records.</li>
      <li>Scan [Decadal] for date issues and any other statistical work.</li>
      <li class="sc">Adjust work allocation if necessary.</li>
      <li>Run stats scan monthly to assess UCF usage and errors rates per transcriber. Advise SC.</li>
      <li>Receive and review data error reports from researchers and pass to SC if action needed.</li>
      <li class="sc">Receive and review data error reports from CC and pass to Transcriber if action needed and latter still active.</li>
      <li class="tr">Receive and review data error reports from SC and action.</li>
      <li class="sc">Make correction if transcriber inactive.</li>
    </ol>
